<item>
            <title>[LU-15840] LOV should return st_blocks=1 for HSM released file</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15840</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The MDT will return st_blocks=1 for a HSM released file.&lt;br/&gt;
The LOV layer should also return st_blocks=1 for a HSM released file in the call -&amp;gt;coo_attr_get.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Otherwise this caused tools like tar then to consider the file as fully sparse and to archive it as is without attempting to acess/restore its content.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
